Class SimpleIntervalModel

java.lang.Object
  org.zkoss.zul.AbstractChartModel

All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, IntervalModel, org.zkoss.zul.ChartModel
public class SimpleIntervalModel
extends org.zkoss.zul.AbstractChartModel
implements IntervalModel

A Band data model implementation of IntervalModel. A Band model is an N series of (from, to) data objects mainly to define some periods of time or some bands between to values. you need tp set some style data in a map for each series to define color, zIndex or xIndex to be used for band representation

Author:
Alain G
